title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 9 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 9 2022
description:
Bill O'Reilly joins Clay and Buck to cover all the day's top news. Washington Commanders Defensive Coordinator Jack Del Rio slams Democrats on BLM/January 6th comparison, media covers his comments more than the attempt on Kavanaugh's life. Ilya Shapiro joins Clay and Buck to tell the story of why he resigned from Georgetown. C&B will watch the Jan. 6th hearing so you don't have to! Whatever happens will be blown away by new inflation numbers tomorrow.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
